==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Foot pound
<hw>Foot" pound`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <fld>(Mech.)</fld> <def>A unit of
energy, or work, being equal to the work done in raising one pound
avoirdupois against the force of gravity through a vertical distance of
one foot.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><-- p. 581 --></p>

